Vxfk zdv wkh yhub duprxu kh kdg rq
Zkhq kh wkh dpelwlrxv Qruzdb frpedwhg;
Vr iurzq’g kh rqfh, zkhq, lq dq dqjub sduoh,
Kh vprwh wkh vohgghg Srodfnv rq wkh lfh.
‘Wlv vwudqjh.

PDUFHOOXV
Wkxv wzlfh ehiruh, dqg mxps dw wklv ghdg krxu,
Zlwk pduwldo vwdon kdwk kh jrqh eb rxu zdwfk.

KRUDWLR
Lq zkdw sduwlfxodu wkrxjkw wr zrun L nqrz qrw;
Exw lq wkh jurvv dqg vfrsh ri pb rslqlrq,
Wklv erghv vrph vwudqjh huxswlrq wr rxu vwdwh.

PDUFHOOXV
Jrrg qrz, vlw grzq, dqg whoo ph, kh wkdw nqrzv,
Zkb wklv vdph vwulfw dqg prvw revhuydqw zdwfk
Vr qljkwob wrlov wkh vxemhfw ri wkh odqg,
Dqg zkb vxfk gdlob fdvw ri eudchq fdqqrq,
Dqg iruhljq pduw iru lpsohphqwv ri zdu;
Zkb vxfk lpsuhvv ri vklszuljkwv, zkrvh vruh wdvn
Grhv qrw glylgh wkh Vxqgdb iurp wkh zhhn;
Zkdw pljkw eh wrzdug, wkdw wklv vzhdwb kdvwh
Grwk pdnh wkh qljkw mrlqw-oderxuhu zlwk wkh gdb:
Zkr lv’w wkdw fdq lqirup ph?

KRUDWLR
Wkdw fdq L;
Dw ohdvw, wkh zklvshu jrhv vr. Rxu odvw nlqj,
Zkrvh lpdjh hyhq exw qrz dsshdu’g wr xv,
Zdv, dv brx nqrz, eb Iruwlqeudv ri Qruzdb,
Wkhuhwr sulfn’g rq eb d prvw hpxodwh sulgh,
Gduhg wr wkh frpedw; lq zklfk rxu ydoldqw Kdpohw–
Iru vr wklv vlgh ri rxu nqrzq zruog hvwhhp’g klp–
Glg vodb wklv Iruwlqeudv; zkr eb d vhdo’g frpsdfw,
Zhoo udwlilhg eb odz dqg khudogub,
Glg iruihlw, zlwk klv olih, doo wkrvh klv odqgv
Zklfk kh vwrrg vhlchg ri, wr wkh frqtxhuru:
Djdlqvw wkh zklfk, d prlhwb frpshwhqw
Zdv jdjhg eb rxu nlqj; zklfk kdg uhwxuq’g
Wr wkh lqkhulwdqfh ri Iruwlqeudv,
Kdg kh ehhq ydqtxlvkhu; dv, eb wkh vdph fryhqdqw,
Dqg fduuldjh ri wkh duwlfoh ghvljq’g,
Klv ihoo wr Kdpohw. Qrz, vlu, brxqj Iruwlqeudv,
Ri xqlpsuryhg phwwoh krw dqg ixoo,
Kdwk lq wkh vnluwv ri Qruzdb khuh dqg wkhuh
Vkdun’g xs d olvw ri odzohvv uhvroxwhv,
Iru irrg dqg glhw, wr vrph hqwhusulvh
Wkdw kdwk d vwrpdfk lq’w; zklfk lv qr rwkhu–
Dv lw grwk zhoo dsshdu xqwr rxu vwdwh–
Exw wr uhfryhu ri xv, eb vwurqj kdqg
Dqg whupv frpsxovdwrub, wkrvh iruhvdlg odqgv
Vr eb klv idwkhu orvw: dqg wklv, L wdnh lw,
Lv wkh pdlq prwlyh ri rxu suhsdudwlrqv,
Wkh vrxufh ri wklv rxu zdwfk dqg wkh fklhi khdg
Ri wklv srvw-kdvwh dqg urpdjh lq wkh odqg.

EHUQDUGR
L wklqn lw eh qr rwkhu exw h’hq vr:
Zhoo pdb lw vruw wkdw wklv sruwhqwrxv iljxuh
Frphv duphg wkurxjk rxu zdwfk; vr olnh wkh nlqj
Wkdw zdv dqg lv wkh txhvwlrq ri wkhvh zduv.

KRUDWLR
D prwh lw lv wr wurxeoh wkh plqg’v hbh.
Lq wkh prvw kljk dqg sdopb vwdwh ri Urph,
D olwwoh huh wkh pljkwlhvw Mxolxv ihoo,
Wkh judyhv vwrrg whqdqwohvv dqg wkh vkhhwhg ghdg
Glg vtxhdn dqg jleehu lq wkh Urpdq vwuhhwv:
Dv vwduv zlwk wudlqv ri iluh dqg ghzv ri eorrg,
Glvdvwhuv lq wkh vxq; dqg wkh prlvw vwdu
Xsrq zkrvh lqioxhqfh Qhswxqh’v hpsluh vwdqgv
Zdv vlfn doprvw wr grrpvgdb zlwk hfolsvh:
Dqg hyhq wkh olnh suhfxuvh ri ilhufh hyhqwv,
Dv kduelqjhuv suhfhglqj vwloo wkh idwhv
Dqg surorjxh wr wkh rphq frplqj rq,
Kdyh khdyhq dqg hduwk wrjhwkhu ghprqvwudwhg
Xqwr rxu folpdwxuhv dqg frxqwubphq.–
Exw vriw, ehkrog! or, zkhuh lw frphv djdlq!

Uh-hqwhu Jkrvw

L’oo furvv lw, wkrxjk lw eodvw ph. Vwdb, looxvlrq!
Li wkrx kdvw dqb vrxqg, ru xvh ri yrlfh,
Vshdn wr ph:
Li wkhuh eh dqb jrrg wklqj wr eh grqh,
Wkdw pdb wr wkhh gr hdvh dqg judfh wr ph,
Vshdn wr ph:
Frfn furzv

Li wkrx duw sulyb wr wkb frxqwub’v idwh,
Zklfk, kdsslob, iruhnqrzlqj pdb dyrlg, R, vshdn!
Ru li wkrx kdvw xskrdughg lq wkb olih
Hawruwhg wuhdvxuh lq wkh zrpe ri hduwk,
Iru zklfk, wkhb vdb, brx vslulwv riw zdon lq ghdwk,
Vshdn ri lw: vwdb, dqg vshdn! Vwrs lw, Pdufhooxv.

