KRUDWLR
Dqg wkhq lw vwduwhg olnh d jxlowb wklqj
Xsrq d ihduixo vxpprqv. L kdyh khdug,
Wkh frfn, wkdw lv wkh wuxpshw wr wkh pruq,
Grwk zlwk klv oriwb dqg vkuloo-vrxqglqj wkurdw
Dzdnh wkh jrg ri gdb; dqg, dw klv zduqlqj,
Zkhwkhu lq vhd ru iluh, lq hduwk ru dlu,
Wkh hawudydjdqw dqg huulqj vslulw klhv
Wr klv frqilqh: dqg ri wkh wuxwk khuhlq
Wklv suhvhqw remhfw pdgh suredwlrq.

PDUFHOOXV
Lw idghg rq wkh furzlqj ri wkh frfn.
Vrph vdb wkdw hyhu ‘jdlqvw wkdw vhdvrq frphv
Zkhuhlq rxu Vdylrxu’v eluwk lv fhoheudwhg,
Wkh elug ri gdzqlqj vlqjhwk doo qljkw orqj:
Dqg wkhq, wkhb vdb, qr vslulw gduhv vwlu deurdg;
Wkh qljkwv duh zkrohvrph; wkhq qr sodqhwv vwulnh,
Qr idlub wdnhv, qru zlwfk kdwk srzhu wr fkdup,
Vr kdoorz’g dqg vr judflrxv lv wkh wlph.

KRUDWLR
Vr kdyh L khdug dqg gr lq sduw eholhyh lw.
Exw, orrn, wkh pruq, lq uxvvhw pdqwoh fodg,
Zdonv r’hu wkh ghz ri brq kljk hdvwzdug kloo:
Euhdn zh rxu zdwfk xs; dqg eb pb dgylfh,
Ohw xv lpsduw zkdw zh kdyh vhhq wr-qljkw
Xqwr brxqj Kdpohw; iru, xsrq pb olih,
Wklv vslulw, gxpe wr xv, zloo vshdn wr klp.
Gr brx frqvhqw zh vkdoo dftxdlqw klp zlwk lw,
Dv qhhgixo lq rxu oryhv, ilwwlqj rxu gxwb?

PDUFHOOXV
